      "description": "A car with real presence and plenty of story left to tell, this one has the kind of honest, broken-in character that makes it stand out from sterile commuter traffic. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who appreciates a hands-on project, needs an affordable runabout, or wants a platform with personality and potential. The body lines still carry a confident look, and with the right attention, this could become a rewarding budget build, weekend tinkering companion, or practical spare vehicle. If you like machines with grit, charm, and room for your own vision, this one is worth a look.",
