    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. An honest, straightforward car that\u2019s well-suited for commuting, first-time drivers, or anyone looking for an inexpensive daily driver or project opportunity. If you want affordable wheels without overpaying, this is a smart chance to get on the road for less.",
