      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t a showpiece, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a great little project to tinker with. It\u2019s got character, it\u2019s priced to make sense, and it could be a really smart buy for the right person. If you want something inexpensive and straightforward, come take a look.",
